* Materialized Views\nfor Transformations
** What They Are
***_ Cached query results
***_ Auto-synced with upstream changes
***_ Better for aggregations & joins
** When to Use
***_ Aggregations (sums, averages)
***_ Complex joins
***_ Updates & deletes in source
** SQL Syntax
***_ CREATE OR REPLACE MATERIALIZED VIEW
***_ Standard SELECT with joins/aggs
** Python Syntax
***_ @dp.materialized_view decorator
***_ Returns regular DataFrame
** vs Streaming Tables
***_ Streaming: append-only, low-latency
***_ Materialized: complex queries, updates
@endmindmap
